file.name: componentResponseType.yaml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.0
servers:
  - url: 'https://localhost:8081/devonfw-server/services/rest'
info:
  title: Devon Example
  description: Example of a API definition
  version: 1.0.0
paths:
  /sampledatamanagement/v1/sampledata/customSearch/:
    post:
      summary: 'Delegates to {@link Moredatamanagement#findMoreDataEtos}.'
      description: Return SampleData that fits the filter.
      operationId: findCustomSampleDataEtos
      responses:
        '200':
          description: List of SampleData's.
          content:
            image/png:
              schema:
                type: array
                items:
                  $ref: '#/components/schemas/SampleData'
      requestBody:
        $ref: '#/components/requestBodies/SampleData'
      tags:
        - searchCriteria
        - paginated
components:
  schemas:
    SampleData:
      x-component: sampledatamanagement
      type: object
      properties:
        name:
          type: string
          maxLength: 100
          minLength: 0
          description: Name string.
      required:
        - name
  requestBodies:
    SampleData:
      content:
        application/json:
          schema:
            $ref: '#/components/schemas/SampleData'
      required: true

Error: notImplemented: path "/sampledatamanagement/v1/sampledata/customSearch/": post: responses: 200: contents: unsupported content types: [image/png]
